<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:RiceYield.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/RiceYield.png/220px-RiceYield.png" width="220" height="132" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/RiceYield.png/330px-RiceYield.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/RiceYield.png/440px-RiceYield.png 2x" data-file-width="1600" data-file-height="960" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
